name: Acoustic for Autism, Volume 1
description:
The goal of Acoustic for Autism is to educate, promote tolerance and understanding, and to help raise funds for non-profit autism organizations – using the power of music.  Volume one contains 12 songs carefully collected to express this philosophy.  All proceeds go directly to non-profits who offer support to children and families affected by autism.  

1. Chris Trapper - Across the World
2. Kris Delmhorst - Light of the Light
3. Anuhea - Endlessly
4. Analogue Transit - Breathe
5. Elizabeth Lorrey - Awakening
6. The Rafters - Every Mile
7. Cormac McCarthy - This Beautiful Place
8. Boondogs - I Don't Belong
9. Dennis Crommett - Oranges and Reds
10. Amber Rubarth - Rough Cut
11. Mulehead - Feathers in the Wind
12. Imua Garza - It's Not Too Late
